Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.67,0:00:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,《綠箭俠》前情提要\N{\b0\fs12}Previously, on "Arrow..."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.28,0:00:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但有些事情永遠不能提起\N{\b0\fs12}But there are some things that must never be spoken of.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.18,0:00:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎能不告訴我  馬爾科姆•梅林是我父親\N{\b0\fs12}How could you not tell me Malcolm Merlyn was my father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.93,0:00:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,莎拉  你不是個殺手\N{\b0\fs12}Sara, you're not a killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.98,0:00:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我該是什麼就是什麼\N{\b0\fs12}I am what I need to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.65,0:00:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊  你是個危險的人\N{\b0\fs12}Roy, you're dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.81,0:00:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,有些人就是扭曲\N{\b0\fs12}Some people are just broken, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.94,0:00:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會讓羅伊遇上發生在斯萊德身上的事\N{\b0\fs12}I am not letting what happened to Slade happen to Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.67,0:00:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我想的東西嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Is that what I think it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.14,0:00:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,米拉庫魯  我們要用它製造解藥\N{\b0\fs12}Mirakuru. We're going to use it to make a cure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.53,0:00:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有改變嗎\N{\b0\fs12}No change?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.28,0:00:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有\N{\b0\fs12}Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.28,0:00:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好多血和好多米拉庫魯混在一起\N{\b0\fs12}So much blood mixed in with so much Mirakuru,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.06,0:00:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道那是好事還是壞事\N{\b0\fs12}I don't know if it's good or bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.81,0:00:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我們真的很需要解藥\N{\b0\fs12}We could really use that cure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.19,0:00:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我今早和凱特琳聊過了\N{\b0\fs12}I talked to Caitlin this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.56,0:00:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他們在努力\N{\b0\fs12}They're working on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.41,0:00:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,沒提到伊莎貝爾•羅切夫的死嗎\N{\b0\fs12}No mention on Isabel Rochev's death?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.49,0:00:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,完全沒有  我也沒指望有華麗的訃告\N{\b0\fs12}Not a thing. I wasn't expecting a glowing obituary,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.40,0:00:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但她是失蹤一周的福布斯500強總裁\N{\b0\fs12}but she's a Fortune 500 CEO that's been missing for a week now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.32,0:00:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我還以為她會占點篇幅呢\N{\b0\fs12}You'd think she'd have some column inches.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.03,0:01:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他躺在那我覺得有些害怕\N{\b0\fs12}Does the fact that him lying there freaks me out a little
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.39,0:01:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,這說明我是個壞人嗎\N{\b0\fs12}make me a bad person?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.65,0:01:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,費利西蒂  我覺得世界上沒有什麼力量\N{\b0\fs12}Felicity, I don't think there's a force on earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.97,0:01:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,能讓你變成壞人\N{\b0\fs12}that can make you a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.07,0:01:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,但我餓壞了\N{\b0\fs12}But I am starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.26,0:01:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,一起吃晚餐嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.09,0:01:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.17,0:01:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但是不去大貝利[大肚]漢堡店\N{\b0\fs12}No Big Belly burger, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.43,0:01:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,會讓我肚子變大\N{\b0\fs12}It's giving me a big belly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.50,0:01:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那就吃壽司\N{\b0\fs12}Sushi, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.87,0:01:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那就吃壽司\N{\b0\fs12}Sushi, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.26,0:01:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你都昏迷了怎麼還能嚇我...\N{\b0\fs12}How can you be unconscious and freak me out at the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.65,0:01:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,一跳啊\N{\b0\fs12}time?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.94,0:01:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊\N{\b0\fs12}Roy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.70,0:01:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\b0\fs12}Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.31,0:01:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你嚇壞我了\N{\b0\fs12}Oh, you scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.43,0:01:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊\N{\b0\fs12}Roy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.15,0:01:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,忘記拿手機了\N{\b0\fs12}Forgot my phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.69,0:01:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊  聽著\N{\b0\fs12}Roy, listen--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.03,0:01:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,狄格\N{\b0\fs12}Dig!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.30,0:01:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-你沒事吧  -快去\N{\b0\fs12}- You ok? - Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.13,0:01:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊\N{\b0\fs12}Roy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.78,0:02:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊\N{\b0\fs12}Roy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.67,0:02:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事\N{\b0\fs12}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.80,0:02:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,讓開  讓開  讓開\N{\b0\fs12}Move, move, move, move, move, move, move, move!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.94,0:02:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,讓開\N{\b0\fs12}Move, move!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.66,0:02:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得羅伊沒事吧\N{\b0\fs12}You think Roy's ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,別告訴我你現在在想羅伊的事\N{\b0\fs12}Please tell me that you're not thinking about Roy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.61,0:02:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我們終於獨處了  躺在\N{\b0\fs12}We're finally alone, in bed,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.55,0:02:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,一家豪華酒店房間裡的床上\N{\b0\fs12}in a very nice hotel room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.37,0:02:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你付不起這豪華酒店的房費\N{\b0\fs12}A hotel room that you couldn't afford.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:02:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我和這裡的經理有點關係\N{\b0\fs12}I have something of a history with the manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.30,0:03:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我還真是想不到啊\N{\b0\fs12}I can only imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我有次就是倒的這間房裡的垃圾\N{\b0\fs12}I think I trashed this specific room once.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.23,0:03:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,但是特權用完了\N{\b0\fs12}But favors run out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.21,0:03:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我們該考慮找一個更長久的地方\N{\b0\fs12}We should think about getting a more permanent place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.78,0:03:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我們\N{\b0\fs12}We?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.91,0:03:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你和勞蕾爾住一起可能也膩了\N{\b0\fs12}Well, you're probably getting tired of staying with Laurel,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.07,0:03:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,既然羅伊在鑄造廠\N{\b0\fs12}and we can't sleep in the foundry
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.87,0:03:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我們也不能睡在那裡  所以...\N{\b0\fs12}now that Roy's there, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不過  我是說"我們"\N{\b0\fs12}But, I mean, "We,"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.54,0:03:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你這是讓我搬去和你同居嗎\N{\b0\fs12}now you're asking me to move in with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.67,0:03:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你的手機響了\N{\b0\fs12}Hey, your phone's ringing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.38,0:03:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\b0\fs12}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.75,0:03:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我倆的手機都在響\N{\b0\fs12}Okay, both our phones are ringing,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.22,0:03:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,這從來不是好事\N{\b0\fs12}that's never good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.22,0:03:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}費利西蒂  來電
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.23,0:03:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,出什麼事了\N{\b0\fs12}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.52,0:04:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道  前一分鐘他還昏迷不醒\N{\b0\fs12}I don't know. One minute he's comatose,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來他就掀翻了電腦設備\N{\b0\fs12}the next, he's flipping over computer equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.37,0:04:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他比斯萊德在你家還失控\N{\b0\fs12}He was a lot more out of control than Slade was at your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.62,0:04:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他看起來像羅伊  但他不是羅伊\N{\b0\fs12}He looked like Roy, but he...wasn't Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.53,0:04:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得他要去哪裡\N{\b0\fs12}Where do you think he's headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.73,0:04:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道  但我們得找到他\N{\b0\fs12}I don't know, but we have to find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,出乎大家意料之外\N{\b0\fs12}Despite everyone's predictions,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.87,0:04:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你在最近的投票中超過了塞巴斯蒂安•布拉德\N{\b0\fs12}you've managed to pull ahead of Sebastian Blood in recent polls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.31,0:04:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我們所傳達的信息和選民產生了共鳴\N{\b0\fs12}Yes. I think our message is resonating with the voters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.12,0:04:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,星城人民知道我高瞻遠矚\N{\b0\fs12}The people of Starling know that I have a vision,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,並擁有經驗豐富的機構  能讓夢想成真\N{\b0\fs12}and the experienced apparatus to make that vision a reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.05,0:04:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得人民該給你  而不是布拉德議員\N{\b0\fs12}What would you say is the main reason
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.33,0:04:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,投票的主要原因是什麼\N{\b0\fs12}they should vote for you over Alderman Blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.43,0:04:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,這個嘛\N{\b0\fs12}Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.76,0:04:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,布拉德議員沒有孩子\N{\b0\fs12}Alderman Blood isn't a parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.32,0:04:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,作為父母的重點\N{\b0\fs12}And the soul of being a parent
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.87,0:04:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,就是保證孩子擁有美好的未來\N{\b0\fs12}is making sure that your children have a bright future.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.65,0:04:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我很幸運  我為我的孩子安排了美好的未來\N{\b0\fs12}And I've been very lucky to be able to do that for my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.48,0:04:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  年度最佳母親\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah. Mother of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我正在接受採訪呢\N{\b0\fs12}Uh, we're in the middle of an interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那我長話短說\N{\b0\fs12}Oh, I'll keep it short.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.91,0:04:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能在威登酒吧召開集會\N{\b0\fs12}You can't have your rally at Verdant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.09,0:04:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我唯一擁有的未被你荼毒的地方\N{\b0\fs12}It's the only place I have that hasn't been poisoned by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,能讓我們聊會兒嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Can you give me one moment, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,關掉\N{\b0\fs12}Turn it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.30,0:05:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,西婭  我知道你很生氣\N{\b0\fs12}Thea, I know you're upset,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.05,0:05:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你有理由如此\N{\b0\fs12}and you have every right to be,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.45,0:05:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但我們得去別的地方聊\N{\b0\fs12}but we need to talk somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.10,0:05:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想跟你聊了  我只是過來告訴你\N{\b0\fs12}I'm done talking. I just came by to tell you,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.29,0:05:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你想用我的酒吧是絕對不可能的事\N{\b0\fs12}it'll be a cold day in hell before you can use my club.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.25,0:05:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我們不能集會前一天突然改變地點\N{\b0\fs12}We can't just change the venue the day before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.38,0:05:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我肯定你能想出辦法的\N{\b0\fs12}I'm sure you can figure something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟  你擁有經驗豐富的機構\N{\b0\fs12}I mean, you have such an experienced apparatus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.81,0:05:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你簽了合同\N{\b0\fs12}You signed a contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.86,0:05:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我還以為你的下限不會更低了呢...\N{\b0\fs12}Just when I thought you couldn't go any lower...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.92,0:05:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你竟然威脅你自己的女兒\N{\b0\fs12}You threaten your own daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,莫伊拉\N{\b0\fs12}Moira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.97,0:05:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事\N{\b0\fs12}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.87,0:05:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉讓你看到這些\N{\b0\fs12}Sorry you had to witness that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.42,0:05:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,她被綁架後\N{\b0\fs12}After her abduction,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.27,0:05:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我還以為你倆應該更為親密\N{\b0\fs12}I'd think that the two of you would be closer than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,情況很複雜\N{\b0\fs12}It's a very complicated situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.23,0:05:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我的建議是\N{\b0\fs12}Well, my advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,簡化它\N{\b0\fs12}Simplify it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你要麼做個母親  要麼做候選人\N{\b0\fs12}You have to be either a mother or a candidate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.72,0:05:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,沒法兩全其美\N{\b0\fs12}You can't be both.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.75,0:06:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,現在不行  你不能分散注意\N{\b0\fs12}Not right now. You cannot split your focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.87,0:06:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你說得太對了\N{\b0\fs12}You're absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.76,0:06:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你無精打采時真可愛\N{\b0\fs12}You're really cute when you're mopey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.92,0:06:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是無精打采\N{\b0\fs12}I'm not mopey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.72,0:06:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,無精打采是你的默認狀態  奧利\N{\b0\fs12}Mopey's your default, Ollie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.24,0:06:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,這是你鬱積魅力的一部分\N{\b0\fs12}It's part of your smoldering charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.69,0:06:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我的確有鬱積魅力\N{\b0\fs12}I do have smoldering charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,但你比平常更加無精打采\N{\b0\fs12}But you're more than usual mopey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.21,0:06:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都還好嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Is everything all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.17,0:06:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事\N{\b0\fs12}It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.22,0:06:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利\N{\b0\fs12}Ollie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.02,0:06:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我和湯米出去玩\N{\b0\fs12}Tommy had me out a little bit later
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,回來的有些晚了\N{\b0\fs12}than maybe I should have been, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我有點累了\N{\b0\fs12}I'm wiped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你想讓我走嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Well, you want me to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.98,0:06:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我答應過莎拉要給她輔導三角學的\N{\b0\fs12}I promised Sara I'd help her with her trigonometry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.65,0:07:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼東西\N{\b0\fs12}I don't know what that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.59,0:07:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你很可愛\N{\b0\fs12}You are very cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,睡一會兒吧\N{\b0\fs12}Get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.07,0:07:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,再見\N{\b0\fs12}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.84,0:07:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,再見\N{\b0\fs12}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安  奎恩夫人\N{\b0\fs12}Good night, Mrs. Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.93,0:07:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安\N{\b0\fs12}Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.30,0:07:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你昨晚沒和湯米一起出去\N{\b0\fs12}You didn't go out with Tommy last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.54,0:07:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你偷聽我的整個談話  媽媽\N{\b0\fs12}Thanks for eavesdropping on my entire conversation, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.40,0:07:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真好\N{\b0\fs12}That's--that's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.70,0:07:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,寶貝  你有煩心事\N{\b0\fs12}Sweetheart, something's bothering you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.57,0:07:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,和我說說\N{\b0\fs12}tell me what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸會殺了我的\N{\b0\fs12}Dad's going to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你父親是愛你的\N{\b0\fs12}Your father loves you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我愛你\N{\b0\fs12}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.74,0:07:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我搞砸了\N{\b0\fs12}I screwed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.43,0:07:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,很糟糕\N{\b0\fs12}It's bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事\N{\b0\fs12}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.03,0:08:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我讓一個女孩懷孕了\N{\b0\fs12}I got a girl pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.70,0:08:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,勞蕾爾懷孕了\N{\b0\fs12}Laurel's pregnant?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.35,0:08:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有\N{\b0\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不是勞蕾爾\N{\b0\fs12}Not Laurel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,這太荒唐了\N{\b0\fs12}This is ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我們不能就這麼到處瞎逛\N{\b0\fs12}We can't just ride around all night
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,指望能找到他\N{\b0\fs12}hoping to lay eyes on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.63,0:08:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,-狄格爾  -他不在住處\N{\b0\fs12}- Diggle? - His place is clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我認為他不會回去\N{\b0\fs12}I don't think he's been back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.01,0:08:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,有個電話召急救車去14大街和霍巴特路路口\N{\b0\fs12}Call just went out for an ambulance at 14th and Hobart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.71,0:08:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,有四個人遭到一個\N{\b0\fs12}There's four men seriously assaulted...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.25,0:08:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}14大街與霍巴特路路口
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.47,0:08:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,穿紅色兜帽衫人的襲擊\N{\b0\fs12}by someone wearing a red hoodie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.82,0:08:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,發生了什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.44,0:08:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙突然冒出來  直接就來打我們\N{\b0\fs12}Guy jumped us. Came out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.82,0:08:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙跟打了雞血一樣\N{\b0\fs12}The dude is 'roided out or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.74,0:08:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,瘋狂得很\N{\b0\fs12}Crazy like.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.69,0:09:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,再會  辛\N{\b0\fs12}See ya, Sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.44,0:09:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,再見[西語]\N{\b0\fs12}Adios.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.44,0:09:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,小屁孩\N{\b0\fs12}Yo, Abercrombie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.35,0:09:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  你去哪了\N{\b0\fs12}Hold up. Where you been, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.61,0:09:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我去找過你差不多20次了\N{\b0\fs12}I went over to your place like 20 times.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.14,0:09:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,西婭說你去外地了\N{\b0\fs12}Thea said you skipped town.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.47,0:09:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我去\N{\b0\fs12}Holy crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.92,0:09:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你打架了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Have you been in a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.46,0:09:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,辛  這傢伙在找你麻煩嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Sin, is this guy bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.65,0:09:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不  他很冷靜  真的  你走開吧\N{\b0\fs12}No, no, no, he's chill. Seriously, just step off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.40,0:09:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼問題嗎\N{\b0\fs12}We going to have a problem, guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.47,0:09:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你真要這麼著嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.87,0:09:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,別管他  他沒事\N{\b0\fs12}Just leave him alone, he's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.34,0:09:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼  慫了不說話了\N{\b0\fs12}Oh, what, you got nothing smart to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.76,0:09:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,費利西正在蒂通過遍佈全城的\N{\b0\fs12}Felicity's running facial recognition
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.14,0:09:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,監控攝像頭進行面部識別\N{\b0\fs12}on traffic cameras throughout the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:09:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,也許永遠都完不成\N{\b0\fs12}Which could take forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.60,0:10:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,在羅伊傷害其他人之前我們必須把他打倒\N{\b0\fs12}We need to take Roy down now before he attacks any more people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.04,0:10:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,"我不想見到你這句話"\N{\b0\fs12}What part of "I want nothing to do with you"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.90,0:10:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,哪個字你聽不懂\N{\b0\fs12}are just not understanding?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我是來找莎拉的\N{\b0\fs12}I came by to see Sara.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.73,0:10:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那他呢\N{\b0\fs12}And what about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他在跟蹤我\N{\b0\fs12}He's been stalking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.26,0:10:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他在保護你\N{\b0\fs12}He's protecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.49,0:10:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,因為什麼呢\N{\b0\fs12}From what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德•威爾遜還沒被抓到\N{\b0\fs12}Slade Wilson is still at large.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.15,0:10:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他已經嘗試過傷害你了\N{\b0\fs12}He already tried hurting you once.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.18,0:10:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他沒有傷到我\N{\b0\fs12}He didn't hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他告訴了我真相  你認為是壞事的真相\N{\b0\fs12}He told me the truth, which I know you think is a bad thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.65,0:10:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,其實不是壞事\N{\b0\fs12}but it's actually not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.96,0:10:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,如果意味著我要失去你那就是\N{\b0\fs12}It is if it costs me you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.33,0:10:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你的謊言才是\N{\b0\fs12}Your lies did that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.49,0:10:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,現在  我要去樓上的儲藏室\N{\b0\fs12}Now, I'm going to go upstairs to the stock room,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有人拿小酒杯打我\N{\b0\fs12}and if I get attacked by some shot glasses,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.83,0:10:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己會報警的\N{\b0\fs12}I'll call 911.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.25,0:10:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你照顧她\N{\b0\fs12}Thanks for taking care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.35,0:10:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,幸運的是  她不像你那麼善於消失\N{\b0\fs12}Lucky for me, she's not as good at disappearing as you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.76,0:10:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我去去就回\N{\b0\fs12}I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.80,0:10:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你見到西婭了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Have you seen Thea?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你眼睛怎麼了\N{\b0\fs12}What happened to your eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.39,0:10:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼  化個妝掩蓋一下就好\N{\b0\fs12}It's ok. I could cover it with make-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.37,0:10:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我有那手藝的話\N{\b0\fs12}If I work make-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.24,0:10:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的\N{\b0\fs12}It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,誰幹的\N{\b0\fs12}Who did this to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.66,0:10:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,說來話長\N{\b0\fs12}It's a long story.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.43,0:10:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我問你是誰幹的\N{\b0\fs12}I asked you who.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.78,0:10:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊\N{\b0\fs12}Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.58,0:11:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他現在腦子不正常\N{\b0\fs12}But he's not right in the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,他被人注射了什麼東西\N{\b0\fs12}He got injected with something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.94,0:11:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,也許是藥吧  但那讓他變得很強壯\N{\b0\fs12}A drug, I don't know, but it made him strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.23,0:11:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,就像  漫畫裡的英雄那樣\N{\b0\fs12}Like, comic book strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.28,0:11:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道那聽上去很瘋狂\N{\b0\fs12}Look, I know it sounds nuts--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.61,0:11:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,其實不會\N{\b0\fs12}It really doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.16,0:11:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,莎拉  羅伊是個朋友\N{\b0\fs12}Sara, Roy's a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.57,0:11:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他需要幫助  而不是被打\N{\b0\fs12}He needs help, not a beat down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.23,0:11:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我等會給你回電話\N{\b0\fs12}I'll have to call you right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.36,0:11:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要留下嗎  布拉德先生\N{\b0\fs12}Do you want me to stay, Mr. Blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.82,0:11:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不用  謝謝你\N{\b0\fs12}No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的\N{\b0\fs12}I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.13,0:11:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我的新保鏢\N{\b0\fs12}My new body man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.95,0:11:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他有點擔心過頭\N{\b0\fs12}He's a little over-protective.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.06,0:11:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-請坐  -不用  謝謝\N{\b0\fs12}- Please. - No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.24,0:11:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不得不說你的來訪有點突然\N{\b0\fs12}I'd say this visit is unexpected,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.56,0:11:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,但我會有什麼說什麼\N{\b0\fs12}but I despise understatements.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.97,0:11:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我要退出競選了\N{\b0\fs12}I'm dropping out of the race.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.32,0:11:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我會在今晚的集會上發布敗選演說\N{\b0\fs12}I'm making a concession speech at my rally tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.42,0:11:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,上一輪投票後你是領先的\N{\b0\fs12}You're ahead in the latest polls.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,即便是持最懷疑態度的專家\N{\b0\fs12}Even the most skeptical pundits
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.54,0:11:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,都說你很可能勝出\N{\b0\fs12}are saying you could actually pull this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.14,0:11:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我是出於禮貌才當面告訴你這事的\N{\b0\fs12}I felt I owed you the courtesy of informing you in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.76,0:11:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不需要向你解釋什麼\N{\b0\fs12}I don't, however, owe you an explanation as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.55,0:11:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  你說得對\N{\b0\fs12}No, you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.06,0:12:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我希望你解釋一下\N{\b0\fs12}But I'd appreciate one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.43,0:12:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,無論你是要做什麼事  莫伊拉\N{\b0\fs12}What you're doing, Moira,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.00,0:12:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,只要會給我帶來好處\N{\b0\fs12}as much as it benefits me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎都不合常理\N{\b0\fs12}doesn't really make much sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.69,0:12:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是為了我的女兒\N{\b0\fs12}It's my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.15,0:12:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,這個時候  她比星城更需要我\N{\b0\fs12}At the moment, she needs me more than Starling does.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.06,0:12:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你做了正確的事\N{\b0\fs12}Well, you're doing the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.02,0:12:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我要改變這座城市  莫伊拉\N{\b0\fs12}I'm going to change this city, Moira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.80,0:12:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,新的時代即將開啟\N{\b0\fs12}A new day is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.30,0:12:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,一個更好的時代\N{\b0\fs12}A better day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.92,0:12:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,對我們所有人\N{\b0\fs12}For all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.82,0:12:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道有些事情讓人喪氣  寶貝\N{\b0\fs12}I know things seem bleak, sweetheart,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,但我們會解決的  我保證\N{\b0\fs12}but we're going to figure this out, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.31,0:12:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽  這公平嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Mom, does it seem fair?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.85,0:12:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,犯了\N{\b0\fs12}To make...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.86,0:12:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,一個錯誤  那感覺\N{\b0\fs12}one mistake, and it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.91,0:12:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,就好像我的整個生命已經結束了\N{\b0\fs12}feels like my entire life is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你的生活才沒有完蛋\N{\b0\fs12}Oh, your life is far from over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.44,0:13:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你確定孩子是你的嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Are you sure it's yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.12,0:13:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你有錢  奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}Where there is money, Oliver,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.57,0:13:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,就會有人想來占你的便宜\N{\b0\fs12}there are people looking to take advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.05,0:13:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,她不是那種人  她是個好人  媽媽\N{\b0\fs12}She's not that type of person. She's a good person, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.51,0:13:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,她是...\N{\b0\fs12}She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.46,0:13:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\b0\fs12}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.28,0:13:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道該怎麼辦  我該怎麼辦呢\N{\b0\fs12}I don't know what to do. What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.23,0:13:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,人非聖賢孰能無錯  奧利弗  我希望\N{\b0\fs12}We all make mistakes, Oliver. And I had hoped
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.26,0:13:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,有天你也會原諒我所犯下的錯誤\N{\b0\fs12}that one day you'd forgive me for any that I might make, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.03,0:13:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  我出去下\N{\b0\fs12}All right, um, I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.94,0:13:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,辛在威登酒吧  14街和霍巴特街路口\N{\b0\fs12}Verdant, 14th and Hobart,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.47,0:13:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,還有另一個酒吧都有看到他\N{\b0\fs12}and the bar Sin spotted him at.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.82,0:13:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,-他好像正往東走  -東邊有什麼\N{\b0\fs12}- He looks to be moving east. - What's east?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.33,0:13:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,奎恩家的豪宅\N{\b0\fs12}Queen mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.20,0:13:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他還記得西婭的住處\N{\b0\fs12}If he still remembers where Thea lives--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.88,0:13:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,以前的住處\N{\b0\fs12}well, used to live,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.89,0:13:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,但羅伊並不知道...\N{\b0\fs12}but Roy doesn't know that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.95,0:13:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,或許他的人性並沒有完全泯滅\N{\b0\fs12}There might be something in Roy still left in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,或許他只是碰巧往東走而已\N{\b0\fs12}Or it's just a coincidence that he's moving east.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:13:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道這件事牽扯到了辛\N{\b0\fs12}Ahem. I know that Sin's involved,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:13:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,但不要讓它影響你的判斷\N{\b0\fs12}but don't let that cloud your judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.38,0:14:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,別忘了以前羅伊可是經常影響你的判斷\N{\b0\fs12}Well, don't let the fact that this used to be Roy cloud yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,辛\N{\b0\fs12}Sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.00,0:14:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我找到羅伊了\N{\b0\fs12}I found Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.55,0:14:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你說了回家去\N{\b0\fs12}Well, I thought I told you to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.13,0:14:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我就在家這兒呢\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah, that's where I am right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.07,0:14:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,還有他\N{\b0\fs12}And so is he.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.51,0:14:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊\N{\b0\fs12}Roy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.62,0:14:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他不在這兒\N{\b0\fs12}He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.78,0:15:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我是奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}It's Oliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.93,0:15:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是我啊\N{\b0\fs12}It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.12,0:15:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你現在之所以這樣\N{\b0\fs12}What you're doing right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.99,0:15:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,全都是因為米拉庫魯\N{\b0\fs12}it's because of the Mirakuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.28,0:15:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你是個好人  羅伊\N{\b0\fs12}You're a good person, Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.87,0:15:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你的良知和靈魂還在\N{\b0\fs12}You have a conscience and a soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,利用這些來頑強抗爭  你能做到的\N{\b0\fs12}I need you to use those and fight this. You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.31,0:15:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,把箭放下  放下\N{\b0\fs12}Drop the arrow, drop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.49,0:15:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不要\N{\b0\fs12}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.33,0:16:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚滿月\N{\b0\fs12}A full moon tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.35,0:16:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,所以稀奇古怪的事更可能發生\N{\b0\fs12}That really brings out the whack jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.68,0:16:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好消息是不可能會有更怪的事發生了\N{\b0\fs12}Good news is, it can't get any stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.25,0:16:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我的朋友需要你的幫助\N{\b0\fs12}My friend needs your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.67,0:16:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,看來我錯了  我再打給你\N{\b0\fs12}I was wrong. Got to call you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.07,0:16:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,有些是舊傷復發\N{\b0\fs12}Some of this damage is chronic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.78,0:16:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜是從屋頂上跳下來而引發的\N{\b0\fs12}The cost of jumping off rooftops, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.61,0:16:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我要趕快恢復\N{\b0\fs12}I need to get back on my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.66,0:16:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以給你個支架\N{\b0\fs12}I can give you a brace,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.73,0:16:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,但你走起路來還是會很痛\N{\b0\fs12}but you'll still be in horrendous amounts of pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.53,0:16:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,六個月前  這個藥櫃面臨清空的危險\N{\b0\fs12}Six months ago, this cabinet would have been empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.70,0:16:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,華人三合會想阻礙我們的藥品運輸船\N{\b0\fs12}The Chinese Triad was stopping all of our med shipments--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,後來有個人阻止了他們\N{\b0\fs12}until someone stopped them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.17,0:16:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,從那之後  我一直想找個機會謝謝你\N{\b0\fs12}Ever since, I've been looking for a way to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.58,0:16:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}威登酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.30,0:17:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你非要到處跟著我\N{\b0\fs12}If you're going to have to follow me everywhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.72,0:17:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,至少別躲著  好嗎\N{\b0\fs12}at least don't lurk, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.75,0:17:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我必須盯著你\N{\b0\fs12}I can't let you out of my sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.27,0:17:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你不喜歡去哪兒都見到我\N{\b0\fs12}You're sick of seeing me everywhere you go;
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.68,0:17:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,躲著似乎是個不錯的折中辦法\N{\b0\fs12}lurking seemed like a good compromise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.34,0:17:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,效果不太好啊\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah, well, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.48,0:17:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,家人間和諧相處很難\N{\b0\fs12}Family's hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.79,0:17:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,有時他們是世界上最難相處的\N{\b0\fs12}Sometimes they're the hardest in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.53,0:17:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,相親相愛  團團圓圓\N{\b0\fs12}Loving someone so much and letting them love you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.11,0:17:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你說得對  你還是回去躲著比較好\N{\b0\fs12}You know, you're right... You should go back to lurking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.35,0:17:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我經常跟你家人待在一起\N{\b0\fs12}I've spent a lot of time with your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.70,0:17:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,如果這樣你就覺得能插手我的事了\N{\b0\fs12}If you think that gives you the right to weigh in,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.08,0:17:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你就大錯特錯了\N{\b0\fs12}you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.29,0:17:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,再說了  奧利弗很快就成窮光蛋了\N{\b0\fs12}Plus, Oliver will be out of money soon
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.23,0:17:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你也會失業的\N{\b0\fs12}and you'll be unemployed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.66,0:17:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,可不是\N{\b0\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.97,0:17:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,趁我失業前我得趕緊勸勸你\N{\b0\fs12}I guess I should get this in under the wire.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.91,0:17:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你媽媽並不完美\N{\b0\fs12}You know, your mother isn't perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.18,0:17:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,經常犯錯\N{\b0\fs12}Her judgment definitely isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.64,0:17:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,但她唯一始終如一的就是\N{\b0\fs12}But there's one thing she's consistent about
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.14,0:17:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,她愛你和奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}is that she loves you and Oliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那你覺得這應該為她贏得什麼嗎\N{\b0\fs12}And that should buy her what in your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.49,0:17:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道  西婭\N{\b0\fs12}Well, I don't know, Thea...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.56,0:17:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,但她是你的母親\N{\b0\fs12}But she is your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.71,0:17:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,總該有點兒分量吧\N{\b0\fs12}That should buy her something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.38,0:18:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,要不再給她次機會吧\N{\b0\fs12}A second chance, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.87,0:18:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,全市通緝一名罪犯\N{\b0\fs12}...A citywide man hunt for the perpetrator of an attack
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他造成一名警員重傷\N{\b0\fs12}that left one police officer seriously injured
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.38,0:18:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,一名警員死亡\N{\b0\fs12}and the other dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.80,0:18:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我們將播放旁觀者錄制的現場視頻\N{\b0\fs12}We have video shot by a bystander,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.25,0:18:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,但提醒某些觀眾\N{\b0\fs12}but please be warned that the
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.45,0:18:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}重大新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.75,0:18:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,影像甚是清晰\N{\b0\fs12}footage may be too graphic for some viewers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.14,0:18:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天吶\N{\b0\fs12}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.81,0:18:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,西婭\N{\b0\fs12}Thea...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.39,0:18:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去見個朋友\N{\b0\fs12}I have to go see a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.72,0:18:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你非要跟  那就跟吧\N{\b0\fs12}If you have to follow, follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.66,0:18:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,這些可不會讓你膝蓋好起來\N{\b0\fs12}These aren't going to fix your knee.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.82,0:18:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,它們會讓膝蓋好得快一點\N{\b0\fs12}They'll help it heal faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那痊癒之前呢\N{\b0\fs12}And until then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.85,0:18:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,面部識別有什麼進展嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Where are we with facial recognition?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.63,0:18:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,交通攝像頭拍得不清楚\N{\b0\fs12}Traffic cams can't get a clear shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.03,0:18:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,現在我知道你戴兜帽的原因了\N{\b0\fs12}Now I see why you wear that hood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.47,0:18:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}無人匹配
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.61,0:18:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,費利西蒂  我們要先找到他\N{\b0\fs12}Felicity... We need to find Roy before the police do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,因為員警找到他後會殺了他  而我們不會嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Because they'll kill him and we won't?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.75,0:18:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,尖端科研實驗室正在研究解藥\N{\b0\fs12}S.T.A.R. Labs is working on a cure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.43,0:18:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,或許他們永遠都研究不出來\N{\b0\fs12}Which they may never come up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.33,0:18:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,即便有解藥了  但在這期間\N{\b0\fs12}And even if they do, I mean, how many people
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.90,0:18:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,得會有多少人死在羅伊手上\N{\b0\fs12}are we going to let Roy kill in the meantime?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.47,0:18:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你本來也想殺了海倫娜\N{\b0\fs12}You know, you wanted to kill Helena, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.34,0:18:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,但你找到別的方法了\N{\b0\fs12}You found another way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.38,0:18:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,這是兩回事  你心知肚明\N{\b0\fs12}That was different, and you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.43,0:19:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊體內有米拉庫魯  跟斯萊德一樣\N{\b0\fs12}Roy has the Mirakuru in him, just like Slade.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.86,0:19:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,如果現在你有機會殺死斯萊德\N{\b0\fs12}And if you had a clear shot of Slade right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.65,0:19:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定會下手\N{\b0\fs12}you would take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.38,0:19:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊不是斯萊德\N{\b0\fs12}Roy isn't Slade!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.94,0:19:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊不是羅伊了\N{\b0\fs12}Roy isn't Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.44,0:19:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他已經不是他自己了\N{\b0\fs12}He's not himself anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.60,0:19:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,無法挽救了\N{\b0\fs12}he's too far gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我不相信\N{\b0\fs12}I don't believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.40,0:19:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道你在說些什麼嗎  奧利\N{\b0\fs12}Do you even hear yourself right now, Ollie?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.72,0:19:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,五年前我們就有過一模一樣的對話\N{\b0\fs12}This is the exact conversation that we had five years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.24,0:19:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一不同是那時我們在煉獄島上快凍死了\N{\b0\fs12}except we were freezing on Lian Yu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.97,0:19:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.33,0:19:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,做該做的\N{\b0\fs12}What needs to be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.48,0:19:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,一槍爆頭  米拉庫魯也救不了他\N{\b0\fs12}The Mirakuru won't do anything against a head shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.16,0:19:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,莎拉\N{\b0\fs12}Sara!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.78,0:19:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你母親的集會半小時後就會開始\N{\b0\fs12}Your mother's rally starts in a half an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.38,0:19:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我要是你就趕快開始打扮了\N{\b0\fs12}I'd start getting dressed if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.83,0:19:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,她讓我想起我剛回來的時候\N{\b0\fs12}She reminds me so much of me after I came home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.69,0:20:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都看起來...\N{\b0\fs12}When it just seemed...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.13,0:20:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼都不相信  甚至是希望\N{\b0\fs12}Seemed impossible to believe in anything even resembling hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.84,0:20:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,但你相信了\N{\b0\fs12}But you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.69,0:20:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你相信了\N{\b0\fs12}You did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.13,0:20:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,最終還是相信了\N{\b0\fs12}Eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.09,0:20:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,莎拉也會的\N{\b0\fs12}Sara will, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.16,0:20:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你能來\N{\b0\fs12}Oh, thanks for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.71,0:20:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,今天很冷\N{\b0\fs12}It's chill.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.04,0:20:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那是誰\N{\b0\fs12}Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.26,0:20:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我\N{\b0\fs12}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.58,0:20:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我的影子\N{\b0\fs12}my shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.10,0:20:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,聽著  羅伊有點兒不對勁\N{\b0\fs12}Listen, something is going on with Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道  我見過他  他徹底瘋了\N{\b0\fs12}I know, I saw him. He's totally crazed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.43,0:20:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他到底怎麼了\N{\b0\fs12}What's happening to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.43,0:20:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你還記得聖誕節他放我們鴿子那次嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Do you remember around Christmas when he bailed on us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.60,0:20:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.35,0:20:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他被注射了一種藥\N{\b0\fs12}He got shot up with something, this drug,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.21,0:20:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,這種藥讓他神志不清\N{\b0\fs12}and it's been messing with his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你和我哥哥說過這件事嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Did you tell my brother any of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.47,0:20:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有  為什麼這麼問\N{\b0\fs12}No...why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.75,0:20:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那是他派來盯著我的保鏢\N{\b0\fs12}He's got this bodyguard all over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.59,0:20:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他肯定清楚羅伊的事\N{\b0\fs12}He must know about Roy,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.71,0:21:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,以為羅伊是想找我還是什麼\N{\b0\fs12}think he's coming after me or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.96,0:21:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算怎麼辦\N{\b0\fs12}Well, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.54,0:21:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊\N{\b0\fs12}Roy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.23,0:21:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊  是我\N{\b0\fs12}Roy, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.91,0:21:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我是西婭\N{\b0\fs12}It's Thea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.32,0:21:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,真高興我找到你了\N{\b0\fs12}I'm so glad I found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.28,0:21:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直到處找你\N{\b0\fs12}I've been looking everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.43,0:21:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,這都是我的錯\N{\b0\fs12}This is all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.02,0:21:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我你才變成這樣\N{\b0\fs12}I did this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.55,0:21:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你和我分手是因為你需要幫助\N{\b0\fs12}When you broke up with me, it was a cry for help,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.65,0:21:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,可是我沒有聽你解釋\N{\b0\fs12}and I didn't listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.96,0:21:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我真該受到懲罰\N{\b0\fs12}I should be punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.23,0:21:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我活該受到懲罰\N{\b0\fs12}I deserve to be punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.94,0:21:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,如果別人傷害到你\N{\b0\fs12}Someone hurts you,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.80,0:21:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你就要傷害他們更深\N{\b0\fs12}and you hurt them worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.68,0:21:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,要無休止地傷害他們\N{\b0\fs12}You hurt them permanently.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.35,0:21:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你應該殺了我\N{\b0\fs12}You should just kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.47,0:21:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,殺了我\N{\b0\fs12}Kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.63,0:21:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,殺了我\N{\b0\fs12}Kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.78,0:22:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利弗你去哪了  你接到我的電話了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Oliver, where have you been? Haven't you got any of my calls?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.62,0:22:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我剛才沒時間  怎麼了\N{\b0\fs12}I've been busy. What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.60,0:22:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是你媽媽\N{\b0\fs12}It's your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.09,0:22:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,她會沒事的\N{\b0\fs12}She'll do fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.01,0:22:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不  她不會\N{\b0\fs12}No, she won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.01,0:22:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,這次活動不是為了集結大家\N{\b0\fs12}She's not using this event to rally the troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.53,0:22:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,她是想利用這次機會\N{\b0\fs12}She's using it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.58,0:22:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,告訴大家她要退出競選\N{\b0\fs12}to tell people she's dropping out of the race.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.32,0:22:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}Oliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.50,0:22:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,發生什麼了\N{\b0\fs12}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.11,0:22:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,摩托車事故\N{\b0\fs12}It's a motorcycle accident,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.23,0:22:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是我大意了\N{\b0\fs12}it was stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.98,0:22:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯  如果我算的沒錯\N{\b0\fs12}Yes, this would be the second accident in as many weeks,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.95,0:22:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,這是幾周以來的第二次事故了\N{\b0\fs12}if my math is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.43,0:22:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,馬克說你要退出競選\N{\b0\fs12}Mark says you're dropping out of the race.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.64,0:22:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,其實我幾個禮拜之前就該就這麼做\N{\b0\fs12}The truth is, I should have done it weeks ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.87,0:22:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,在西婭被綁架之後\N{\b0\fs12}after Thea was abducted.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.10,0:22:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我的全部心思應該放在修復我們的關係上\N{\b0\fs12}My complete focus needs to be on repairing our relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.94,0:22:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽  西婭現在的情形\N{\b0\fs12}Mom, what's happening with Thea right now
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.22,0:22:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不是你沒花時間陪她造成的\N{\b0\fs12}isn't because you weren't spending enough time with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.26,0:23:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,也許不是吧  但是我必須做點兒什麼\N{\b0\fs12}Well, maybe not. I have to do something
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.31,0:23:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道除了這個我還能做什麼\N{\b0\fs12}and I'm not sure what else to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.27,0:23:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,西婭恨你是因為你過去做的那些事\N{\b0\fs12}Thea hates you right now because of the things that you've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.62,0:23:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那些糟糕的事\N{\b0\fs12}Terrible things.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.11,0:23:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,所以讓她看到你做些好事\N{\b0\fs12}So let her see you do something good.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.57,0:23:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,作為一位市長\N{\b0\fs12}As mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.56,0:23:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽  我瞭解一些事\N{\b0\fs12}Mom, I know a little something about...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.38,0:23:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,例如為了這個城市\N{\b0\fs12}sacrificing the people closest to me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.51,0:23:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,犧牲我身邊最親近的人\N{\b0\fs12}for the good of this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.19,0:23:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是你現在應該做的\N{\b0\fs12}It's what you need to do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.63,0:23:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\b0\fs12}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.97,0:23:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\b0\fs12}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.18,0:23:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利弗  我知道\N{\b0\fs12}Oliver, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.01,0:23:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\b0\fs12}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.34,0:24:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我想\N{\b0\fs12}I've known...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.03,0:24:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,從去年開始我就知道了\N{\b0\fs12}since last year, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.60,0:24:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那個計劃實施的那天\N{\b0\fs12}The night of the undertaking,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.01,0:24:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,所有謎題都解開了\N{\b0\fs12}everything became so clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.66,0:24:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,也是從那天開始我晚上再也睡不著\N{\b0\fs12}It was pretty much the night I stopped sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.24,0:24:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,在你想說什麼之前\N{\b0\fs12}Before you say anything else--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.29,0:24:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想說什麼\N{\b0\fs12}There's nothing else to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.57,0:24:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我不需要說什麼\N{\b0\fs12}Nothing I need to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.37,0:24:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,除了告訴你我感到無比驕傲\N{\b0\fs12}Except I could not be more proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.71,0:24:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你要喝點什麼嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Can I have the raise get you anything to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.78,0:24:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,或者吃些東西  這邊請\N{\b0\fs12}Or--or something to eat, perhaps? Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.48,0:24:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利弗在哪\N{\b0\fs12}Where's Oliver?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.63,0:24:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他去替我辦事了\N{\b0\fs12}Ah, he's...running an errand for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.18,0:24:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,剛好我們可以有機會聊一聊\N{\b0\fs12}I thought it would give us a chance to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.24,0:24:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,無意冒犯  奎恩夫人\N{\b0\fs12}With all due respect, um, Mrs. Queen,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.73,0:24:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我和奧利弗之間的事\N{\b0\fs12}what's happening, it's between me and your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.44,0:24:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,當然了\N{\b0\fs12}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.32,0:25:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.47,0:25:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我的調查員給我的一份關於你的檔案\N{\b0\fs12}Oh, I had one of our investigators write up a dossier on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.98,0:25:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  但是預防\N{\b0\fs12}I'm sorry, but it's a necessary
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.20,0:25:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,欺詐性親權索賠是非常有必要的\N{\b0\fs12}precaution against a fraudulent claim of paternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.43,0:25:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子是奧利弗的\N{\b0\fs12}Well, the baby is Oliver's.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.79,0:25:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我對此毫不懷疑\N{\b0\fs12}Oh, of that I have no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.77,0:25:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的調查員調查得很全面\N{\b0\fs12}Our investigators were quite thorough.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.38,0:25:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你能想像到\N{\b0\fs12}But you can imagine
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.77,0:25:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,外面有多少人等著\N{\b0\fs12}how many people my family attracts
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.50,0:25:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,把我們家的事登上新聞\N{\b0\fs12}who are looking for handouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.37,0:25:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是為了錢\N{\b0\fs12}Well, I'm not looking for money.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.25,0:25:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,當然不是\N{\b0\fs12}Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.29,0:25:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我說了我不想要錢\N{\b0\fs12}I told you, I don't want money.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.79,0:25:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那我告訴你\N{\b0\fs12}And I'm telling you
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.49,0:25:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我第一次當奶奶\N{\b0\fs12}that this is my first grandchild.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.23,0:25:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要確保這個孩子有一個美好的未來\N{\b0\fs12}And I want to make certain that he or she has a bright future.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.39,0:25:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,請收下吧\N{\b0\fs12}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.00,0:25:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,這有一百萬\N{\b0\fs12}This is a million dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.10,0:25:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我同樣也希望我兒子有一個美好的未來\N{\b0\fs12}I want to make certain that my son has a bright future as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.78,0:26:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,這一百萬給你\N{\b0\fs12}That money is yours
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.69,0:26:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,前提是你告訴奧利弗孩子沒了\N{\b0\fs12}once you tell Oliver that you've lost the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.00,0:26:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你說什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.13,0:26:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,等你回中央城後再也不要聯繫他\N{\b0\fs12}And another million when you return to Central city,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.51,0:26:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我會再給你一百萬\N{\b0\fs12}never to speak to him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.58,0:26:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以給你一個建議嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Can I offer you some advice,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.26,0:26:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,以一位母親的身份告誡另一位母親\N{\b0\fs12}one mother to another?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.93,0:26:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦事情涉及到你自己的孩子\N{\b0\fs12}When it comes to your children, there is no action
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.23,0:26:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有什麼事情是你做不出來的\N{\b0\fs12}that is inconceivable;
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.17,0:26:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,也沒有什麼決定是你下不了的\N{\b0\fs12}there is no decision that is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.26,0:26:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你會奮不顧身給他他所需要的生活\N{\b0\fs12}You do what you must to provide the life that they need.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.33,0:26:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我認為那二百萬美元\N{\b0\fs12}And I think that $2 million
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.27,0:26:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,可以給我們的孩子提供他們所需要的生活\N{\b0\fs12}is sufficient to provide the life that both our children need.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.18,0:26:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得呢\N{\b0\fs12}Don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.71,0:26:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}支持奎恩競選市長
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.28,0:26:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,當我最初決定參加此次競選時\N{\b0\fs12}When I was first approached about entering this race,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.77,0:26:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得競選成功的機會是如此渺茫\N{\b0\fs12}the prospect of winning seemed a distant,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.42,0:26:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是幾乎不可能的事\N{\b0\fs12}nearly impossible feat.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.55,0:26:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,一個遭受重創的城市\N{\b0\fs12}Now, how could a city that had suffered so much
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.97,0:27:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能寄希望於給它帶來創傷的人\N{\b0\fs12}place its faith in someone so responsible for its suffering?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.58,0:27:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,但是這幾個星期以來\N{\b0\fs12}But as the weeks progressed,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.35,0:27:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那些如你們一樣正直的人\N{\b0\fs12}good people such as you
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.89,0:27:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,表明了你們的態度\N{\b0\fs12}raised your voices
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.01,0:27:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,支援我  於是我想我可以讓這座城市更美好\N{\b0\fs12}in support, and I began to think that I could make a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.91,0:27:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以為拯救這座城市出一份力\N{\b0\fs12}I could help save this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.36,0:27:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}莫伊拉•奎恩支持者聚會
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.72,0:27:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但\N{\b0\fs12}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.50,0:27:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,最近發生的一些事改變了這一切\N{\b0\fs12}recent events have changed things, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.62,0:27:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不過現在我確信我可以讓這座城市更美好\N{\b0\fs12}and now I know I can make a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.66,0:27:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我能有幸當選市長\N{\b0\fs12}And should the honor become mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.93,0:27:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我鄭重地向各位保證\N{\b0\fs12}I promise with every breath I take
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.13,0:27:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}莫伊拉•奎恩支持者聚會
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.01,0:27:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,為了這座城市的美好未來\N{\b0\fs12}To do what is necessary,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.98,0:27:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我將不惜一切代價  不顧一切犧牲\N{\b0\fs12}To sacrifice what is necessary for the good of this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.15,0:28:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,星城是我的家  你們都是我的家人\N{\b0\fs12}Starling City is my home, you are my family,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.15,0:28:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,對我來說沒有什麼比家人更重要\N{\b0\fs12}And there is nothing more important to me than family.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.93,0:28:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝大家\N{\b0\fs12}Thank you, thank you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.50,0:28:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,說得太好了  莫伊拉\N{\b0\fs12}Great speech, Moira.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.72,0:28:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然跟我中意的相差有些遠\N{\b0\fs12}A little too off-book for my liking,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.67,0:28:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,但我們會努力的\N{\b0\fs12}But we'll work on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.77,0:28:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得很好\N{\b0\fs12}I thought it was perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.63,0:28:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我想上來說幾句\N{\b0\fs12}I just wanted to come up here and say a few words.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.43,0:28:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚我很高興我母親能來\N{\b0\fs12}I am so proud to have my mom here tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.02,0:28:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我這間貧民區的威登酒吧\N{\b0\fs12}at my club, Verdant, in the Glades.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.65,0:28:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,她在幹什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.20,0:28:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,她知道這是直播\N{\b0\fs12}She knows this is being televised.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.42,0:28:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,她這是想引羅伊出來\N{\b0\fs12}She's sending a message to Roy, trying to draw him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.32,0:28:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,請為奎恩投票  跟你們的朋友也這麼說\N{\b0\fs12}So vote Queen. Tell your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.15,0:28:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\b0\fs12}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.43,0:28:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,西婭  \N{\b0\fs12}Thea.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.66,0:28:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是為了你\N{\b0\fs12}That was not for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.95,0:28:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,天吶  你真沉\N{\b0\fs12}Oh, God, you're heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.94,0:29:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,真的都是肌肉的重量嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Is this really all muscle?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.05,0:29:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我們還有多少支毒箭\N{\b0\fs12}How many of those venom arrows do we have?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.15,0:29:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-大約20支  -我全都要帶上\N{\b0\fs12}- About 20. - I need all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.85,0:29:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  你確定這樣做好嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Okay. Are you sure that's a good idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.78,0:29:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你膝蓋現在這樣還能穿上戰袍嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Can you even get into those leather pants with that knee?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.76,0:29:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,馬上給我利多卡因\N{\b0\fs12}Lidocaine. Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.76,0:29:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}一種局部麻醉劑
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.84,0:29:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我看一下  上面寫著合適的劑量是\N{\b0\fs12}Let's see, the bottle says the proper dose is...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.75,0:29:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,全部\N{\b0\fs12}Is all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.11,0:29:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得這樣不...\N{\b0\fs12}I don't think that's a good...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.33,0:29:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,說得太棒了  莫伊拉\N{\b0\fs12}Terrific speech, Moira.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.58,0:29:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我們幾年前就應該推選你\N{\b0\fs12}How did we not think of running you years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.18,0:29:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\b0\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.87,0:29:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我能失陪一會嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Can you give me a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.01,0:29:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,當然\N{\b0\fs12}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.84,0:29:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\b0\fs12}Oh, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.01,0:29:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-你得離開了  -不不不\N{\b0\fs12}- You need to go now! - No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.22,0:29:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能丟下我女兒\N{\b0\fs12}I can't leave without my daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.31,0:29:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我會保護好你女兒的\N{\b0\fs12}I'll see to the safety of your daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.80,0:29:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,走  西婭  我們得離開了\N{\b0\fs12}Go, go! Thea, we have to go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.47,0:29:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不  是羅伊\N{\b0\fs12}No, it's Roy!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.18,0:29:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會離開他  他為我而來\N{\b0\fs12}I'm not leaving him! He came here for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.05,0:30:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊\N{\b0\fs12}Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.84,0:30:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊  聽我說\N{\b0\fs12}Roy, listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.85,0:30:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好好聽我說\N{\b0\fs12}Listen to my voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.18,0:30:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道你是怎麼了\N{\b0\fs12}I don't know what's going on with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.50,0:30:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但我堅信我深愛的那個人\N{\b0\fs12}but I have to believe the man I fell in love with
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.37,0:30:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他還活著\N{\b0\fs12}is still inside there, somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.11,0:30:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你要反抗  你很堅強\N{\b0\fs12}You have to fight. You're strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.94,0:30:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你能反抗的  你要反抗\N{\b0\fs12}You can fight this. Fight this!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.99,0:30:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊\N{\b0\fs12}Roy!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.13,0:30:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,把她放下\N{\b0\fs12}Put her down.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.65,0:30:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不要殺他\N{\b0\fs12}Please don't..
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.65,0:30:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他也控制不了\N{\b0\fs12}he can't control it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.78,0:30:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我也沒有辦法\N{\b0\fs12}That's why I don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.57,0:30:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,閃開\N{\b0\fs12}Get out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.14,0:30:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,別這樣\N{\b0\fs12}Don't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.91,0:30:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,殺了我\N{\b0\fs12}Kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.40,0:31:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了\N{\b0\fs12}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.82,0:31:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,殺了我\N{\b0\fs12}Kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.63,0:31:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,千萬不要殺他\N{\b0\fs12}Please don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.99,0:31:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚誰都不會死\N{\b0\fs12}No one dies tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.59,0:31:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但是員警會...\N{\b0\fs12}But he police...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.54,0:31:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,出去\N{\b0\fs12}Go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.91,0:31:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我們會幫助羅伊\N{\b0\fs12}We'll get Roy the help he needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.57,0:31:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我保證  快走\N{\b0\fs12}I promise! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.65,0:31:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,西藏蝮蛇毒\N{\b0\fs12}Tibetan pit viper venom.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.85,0:31:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,常用劑量對他來說沒用  對吧\N{\b0\fs12}A constant dose of that can't be good for you. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.31,0:31:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他會像當初斯萊德那樣昏迷\N{\b0\fs12}It'll keep him sedated like it did Slade.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.83,0:31:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,昏迷到什麼時候\N{\b0\fs12}Until when?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.23,0:31:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我們要是用完毒劑了怎麼辦\N{\b0\fs12}And what happens when we run out?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.25,0:31:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,這又不是非處方藥\N{\b0\fs12}It's not like you can buy this stuff over the counter.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.19,0:31:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,要是在西藏的話  可能可以買到\N{\b0\fs12}Unless you're in Tibet. Then...maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.90,0:31:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我們要照顧好他\N{\b0\fs12}We'll take care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.96,0:31:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想放棄羅伊\N{\b0\fs12}I'm not ready to give up on Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.90,0:31:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,大戰一場之後有誰想吃點東西嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Anyone else crave dim sum after fisticuffs?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.81,0:32:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,都不吃  好吧\N{\b0\fs12}No? Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.88,0:32:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就把餃子都吃了\N{\b0\fs12}Dumplings for one, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.57,0:32:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我本來要殺他的\N{\b0\fs12}I would have killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.22,0:32:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經準備好了\N{\b0\fs12}I was ready to.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.13,0:32:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不是你攔著  他現在已經死了\N{\b0\fs12}He'd be dead right now if you wouldn't have stopped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.51,0:32:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,可他現在沒死\N{\b0\fs12}But he's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.26,0:32:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,這才是關鍵\N{\b0\fs12}That's all that matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.43,0:32:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你說的不對\N{\b0\fs12}That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.31,0:32:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我想殺死他\N{\b0\fs12}I wanted to kill roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.74,0:32:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,因為這才是我該做的\N{\b0\fs12}Because that's what I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.29,0:32:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,這才是我的本性\N{\b0\fs12}That's who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.88,0:32:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我在煉獄中生活了六年\N{\b0\fs12}I spent six years in the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.16,0:32:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我看著惡魔的雙眼\N{\b0\fs12}And I looked into the eyes of the devil
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.14,0:32:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,把我的靈魂交給了他\N{\b0\fs12}and I gave him my soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.45,0:32:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我幫你找回你的靈魂\N{\b0\fs12}Let me help you get it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.39,0:32:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不  你應該找個更好的人\N{\b0\fs12}No, you deserve someone better.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.56,0:32:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,能夠理解你內心深處的人\N{\b0\fs12}Someone who can harness that light that's still inside of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.37,0:32:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但那個人不是我\N{\b0\fs12}But I'm not that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.51,0:32:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,永遠都不會是我\N{\b0\fs12}And I never will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.14,0:32:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,莎拉\N{\b0\fs12}Sara...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.90,0:33:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不要\N{\b0\fs12}Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.47,0:33:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起\N{\b0\fs12}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.12,0:33:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我太在乎你了  所以不能跟你在一起\N{\b0\fs12}I just care about you too much to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.14,0:33:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都還好嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Everything OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.68,0:33:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  只是這一天太不順了\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah. Just had a long day.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.81,0:33:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊怎麼樣了\N{\b0\fs12}How's Roy?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.02,0:33:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他還活著\N{\b0\fs12}Well, he's alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.08,0:33:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不用謝我\N{\b0\fs12}No thanks to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.14,0:33:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你敢擋在我面前真的很勇敢\N{\b0\fs12}You know, that was brave getting between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.73,0:33:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-這需要很大的勇氣  -也未必\N{\b0\fs12}- It took guts. - Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.88,0:33:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你不是真想傷害他\N{\b0\fs12}I knew you wouldn't really hurt him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.28,0:33:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是殺手\N{\b0\fs12}You're not a killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.49,0:33:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼意思\N{\b0\fs12}What's this for?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.65,0:33:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,告別\N{\b0\fs12}Say good-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.69,0:33:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼  等一下  你要去哪\N{\b0\fs12}What? Wait, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.83,0:33:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,去見個老朋友\N{\b0\fs12}To see an old friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.63,0:34:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,這座城市所有的員警都出動了\N{\b0\fs12}We've got every cop in this city canvassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.81,0:34:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-我們會找到這個人的  -謝謝\N{\b0\fs12}- We'll find this guy. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.75,0:34:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你還好嗎\N{\b0\fs12}You OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.13,0:34:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,還行\N{\b0\fs12}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.55,0:34:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你去哪了\N{\b0\fs12}Where were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.33,0:34:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我在一起\N{\b0\fs12}He was with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.56,0:34:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你們倆和好真是太好了\N{\b0\fs12}Glad to see the two of you are getting along again.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.61,0:34:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,西婭\N{\b0\fs12}Thea...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.47,0:34:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊的事你早就知道\N{\b0\fs12}You knew about Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.64,0:34:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.76,0:34:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你才讓你的保鏢跟蹤我\N{\b0\fs12}That's why you had your bodyguard stalking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.78,0:35:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道他到底是怎麼回事\N{\b0\fs12}Somehow, you knew what was going on with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.82,0:35:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我是想保護你\N{\b0\fs12}I'm just trying to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.55,0:35:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,通過不告訴我真相來保護我嗎\N{\b0\fs12}By not telling me the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.30,0:35:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,就跟馬爾科姆•梅林的事一樣\N{\b0\fs12}Just like with Malcolm Merlyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.33,0:35:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,知道嗎  你們兩個\N{\b0\fs12}You know, the two of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.50,0:35:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你們以為有事瞞著我  跟我說謊\N{\b0\fs12}you think you're protecting me by lying
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.48,0:35:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,就是保護我\N{\b0\fs12}and by keeping secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.44,0:35:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但其實那樣才最傷害我\N{\b0\fs12}But that's what's actually hurting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.03,0:35:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你說得很對\N{\b0\fs12}You're absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.27,0:35:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我們需要走出過去重新開始\N{\b0\fs12}We need to turn a new page.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.68,0:35:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,沒那麼簡單\N{\b0\fs12}It's not going to be that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.93,0:35:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,也沒那麼容易\N{\b0\fs12}Or easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.04,0:35:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道  如果真相於我而言容易的話\N{\b0\fs12}I know. If the truth were easy for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.45,0:35:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我們就不會陷入現在這種境地了\N{\b0\fs12}we wouldn't be in this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.96,0:35:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,但首先\N{\b0\fs12}But to start...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.36,0:35:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你和奧利弗都需要知道一件\N{\b0\fs12}there's something about Malcolm that both you and Oliver
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.43,0:35:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,關於馬爾科姆的事\N{\b0\fs12}need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.51,0:35:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,馬爾科姆...\N{\b0\fs12}Malcolm...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.15,0:36:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}Oliver!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.37,0:36:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}Oliver!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.23,0:36:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我得死\N{\b0\fs12}I need to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.12,0:36:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}Oliver!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.59,0:36:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}Oliver!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.45,0:36:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,上次你讓我選擇的時候\N{\b0\fs12}I was dead the last time
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.04,0:36:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我選擇了死亡\N{\b0\fs12}you were offered this choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.52,0:36:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德\N{\b0\fs12}Slade...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.20,0:36:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}Oliver...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.63,0:36:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事\N{\b0\fs12}What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.90,0:36:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直想知道...\N{\b0\fs12}I often wonder how you looked...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.70,0:36:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他用槍指著莎朵把她從我身邊奪走時\N{\b0\fs12}when he pointed the gun at Shado...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.09,0:36:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你是什麼表情\N{\b0\fs12}and took her from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.51,0:36:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你個變態\N{\b0\fs12}You psychopath.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.61,0:36:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,莎朵  莎朵不是你的\N{\b0\fs12}Shado...Shado wasn't yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.49,0:36:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,對  她曾經是你的\N{\b0\fs12}No, she was yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.02,0:36:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,可是後來你選了別的女人沒選她\N{\b0\fs12}Until you chose another woman over her.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.30,0:36:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不是這樣的\N{\b0\fs12}That's not what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.84,0:37:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這樣  就是\N{\b0\fs12}It is what happened! It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.82,0:37:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,她告訴我的\N{\b0\fs12}She told me!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.90,0:37:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你說她是什麼意思  那裡根本沒人\N{\b0\fs12}What do you mean, she? There's nobody there!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.57,0:37:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德\N{\b0\fs12}Slade...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.74,0:37:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,當時你也跟奧利弗一起在島上嗎\N{\b0\fs12}You were on the island with Oliver?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.34,0:37:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我開始以為自己知道什麼是真正的絕望\N{\b0\fs12}I thought I had known true despair,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.75,0:37:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,直到後來遇到了你兒子\N{\b0\fs12}until I met your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.47,0:37:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我信任他...\N{\b0\fs12}I trusted him...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.75,0:37:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,會做出正確的選擇\N{\b0\fs12}to make the right choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.52,0:37:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,現在讓我做出正確的選擇吧\N{\b0\fs12}Let me make the right choice now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.48,0:37:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,殺我吧\N{\b0\fs12}Kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.31,0:37:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,-不  -不要\N{\b0\fs12}- NO! - NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.41,0:37:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,殺我吧  求你了\N{\b0\fs12}Choose me, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.29,0:37:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我會殺你的  奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}I am killing you, Oliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.04,0:37:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不過不會先殺你\N{\b0\fs12}Only more slowly than you would like.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.64,0:37:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不要\N{\b0\fs12}Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.75,0:37:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,選吧\N{\b0\fs12}Choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.86,0:37:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-不要  -選吧\N{\b0\fs12}- Don't-- - Choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.31,0:37:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了\N{\b0\fs12}Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.78,0:37:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,快選\N{\b0\fs12}Choose!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.01,0:37:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我對天發誓  我一定會殺了你\N{\b0\fs12}I swear to God, I am going to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.46,0:37:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不要\N{\b0\fs12}No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.72,0:37:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\b0\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.72,0:38:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,媽...\N{\b0\fs12}Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.37,0:38:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\b0\fs12}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.95,0:38:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,媽  你幹什麼\N{\b0\fs12}Mom, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.96,0:38:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,要結束今晚\N{\b0\fs12}There's only one way
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.89,0:38:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,-只有一個辦法  -不要\N{\b0\fs12}- this night can end. - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.19,0:38:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了  不要\N{\b0\fs12}Please don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.82,0:38:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我們都知道是什麼辦法\N{\b0\fs12}And we both know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.22,0:38:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是  威爾遜先生\N{\b0\fs12}Don't we, Mr. Wilson?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.07,0:38:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,媽  求你了  不要\N{\b0\fs12}Mom! Please, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.22,0:38:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不要殺我的孩子\N{\b0\fs12}Both my children will live.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.16,0:38:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,媽\N{\b0\fs12}Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.82,0:38:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你幹什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.69,0:38:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,媽\N{\b0\fs12}Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.86,0:38:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,西婭  我愛你\N{\b0\fs12}Thea, I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.92,0:38:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,閉上眼睛  孩子\N{\b0\fs12}Close your eyes, baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.29,0:38:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不要\N{\b0\fs12}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.71,0:38:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不要\N{\b0\fs12}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.67,0:38:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你擁有真正的勇氣\N{\b0\fs12}You possess true courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.90,0:38:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉\N{\b0\fs12}I am truly sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.63,0:38:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.64,0:39:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,可是你的勇氣沒有\N{\b0\fs12}You did not pass that on
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.07,0:39:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,傳給你兒子\N{\b0\fs12}to your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.07,0:39:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\b0\fs12}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.38,0:39:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\b0\fs12}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.23,0:39:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這件事結束之前\N{\b0\fs12}There is still one person
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.54,0:39:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,還有一個人\N{\b0\fs12}who has to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.71,0:39:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,必須得死\N{\b0\fs12}before this can end.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.80,0:39:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不要\N{\b0\fs12}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.15,0:39:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,媽\N{\b0\fs12}Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.81,0:39:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,媽  不\N{\b0\fs12}Mom! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.85,0:39:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不  媽\N{\b0\fs12}No! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.28,0:39:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,對  我也很抱歉\N{\b0\fs12}Well, yeah, I'm sorry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.47,0:39:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有什麼我可以幫忙的話...\N{\b0\fs12}Well, listen, if there's ever anything that I can do--
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.09,0:39:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,喂\N{\b0\fs12}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.46,0:40:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是誰\N{\b0\fs12}Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.27,0:40:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是...\N{\b0\fs12}That was, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.22,0:40:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,她失去了孩子\N{\b0\fs12}She lost the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.38,0:40:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,她說自己很傷心\N{\b0\fs12}She said she's sad about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.83,0:40:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,要回中心區的學校去了\N{\b0\fs12}and she's going to go back to school in central city.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.86,0:40:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,她在那邊肯定有家人\N{\b0\fs12}Apparently she has family there.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.35,0:40:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,她肯定很痛苦\N{\b0\fs12}Well, I'm sure this has been very traumatic for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.44,0:40:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但這樣對她也許是最好的\N{\b0\fs12}But it sounds for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.21,0:40:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-是啊  -你沒事吧\N{\b0\fs12}- Sure. - You OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.39,0:40:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事  沒事\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.56,0:40:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我仍然是世界上最幸運的人\N{\b0\fs12}I continue to be the luckiest guy on the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.83,0:40:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,要是...\N{\b0\fs12}What...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.52,0:40:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我該怎麼辦啊  要是...\N{\b0\fs12}What would I have done if she...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.21,0:40:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我還沒做好當爸爸的準備\N{\b0\fs12}I'm not ready to be a dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.49,0:41:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,現在沒有  但總有一天會的\N{\b0\fs12}No. But someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.70,0:41:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我最大的希望\N{\b0\fs12}It's my fondest hope for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.19,0:41:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我很高興我告訴你了\N{\b0\fs12}I'm glad I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.00,0:41:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,要是你不在我身邊\N{\b0\fs12}I don't think that I could have
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.80,0:41:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我一個人肯定不知道怎麼辦\N{\b0\fs12}gotten through something like this without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.92,0:41:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我會一直在你身邊的\N{\b0\fs12}You're never without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.29,0:41:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我的乖兒子\N{\b0\fs12}My beautiful boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.58,0:41:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,媽...\N{\b0\fs12}It's, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.55,0:41:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我愛你\N{\b0\fs12}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.47,0:41:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我愛你\N{\b0\fs12}I love you.
